node.text:
... filmed a whole load of fun stuff the other day! Can’t wait to share it with you.. we originally didn’t plan to record any Christmas songs but @politemike and @hannahvofficial had other ideas...
#christmascountdown #feelingunusuallyfestive 🎄😆

💙
📸 @tomsmarte

Had such a great time performing this tune at @djtrevornelson's Soul Christmas at @royalalberthall last night with @bbcconcertorchestra and @troy__miller! 🎄 
Amazing work by the rest of the performers too @rayblk @lauramvula @vulavox @therealeve @emelisande @sammhenshaw @tonymomrelle
Netherlands! 🇳🇱 I'll be back to see you all at @paaspopfestival in April. Get your tickets now!
Looking forward to playing this out on the road in April! 😊 There's still a few tickets left if you've not got yours yet and want to hear this live.. link at the TOUR highlight.
So so good to do another @capitalofficial jingle bell ball with @jonasblue. Great to catch up with the team.. thanks so much for having me..

Working hard here to get the word out about my shows across Europe. Let me know if you’re coming! Why not be an angel and tag a friend who should come along to one of the shows 😆 Love Jp x #outtakes #fails
Had an amazing time at the British Fashion Awards last night.. thanks for the invite @riverisland! 🙏🏻

Thank you to the Royal Northern College of music for having me! Special to shout out to Andy Stott and @wayneellington7 for bringing this to life. So great to meet all the incredibly talented students .. was an honour to be a part of it.... This is my cover of ‘stand by me’ by the great Ben E king... would you guys be up for a full live recording of this track? Much love, Jp x
Had a chat with the folks at @@mahogany  about my journey so far... give it a watch if you fancy! 😊 Link in the story!

Proof that music brings people together 🙏 This brightened up my day. This amazing group of children put some beautiful harmonies over a cover I did of swing low sweet chariot. Thank you @ms.laceysclassroom for sharing this .... ❤️
Check out the live version of The Reason Why that me and the gents recorded while rehearsing for tour a few weeks back..!

Great news! Been doing a bit of housekeeping and we’ve finally managed to get one of my old EPs back up on streaming sites.. 🙌🏻 When The Darkness Comes EP is available again now at the MUSIC highlight on my profile!

Lightbulb moments... 💡
📸 @1883magazine
What was your first reaction to the stripped back versions of The Reason Why? ... apparently mine was knee slapping. 😂
The acoustic and piano versions of The Reason Why are OUT NOW! 🙌🏻
Tomorrow.. brand new acoustic and piano versions of The Reason Why! Looking forward to you hearing them.. 🙌🏻
The devil's in the details.. 😂 Working away at something special for you all with @hannahvofficial..
Thinking back to last month's tour.. let's see your pictures, tag me in your story! 😊 Can't wait to do it all over again next year..
Had a little chat with @1883magazine about my journey in music.. give it a read at the link in my story. 😊
See you on tonight at 6 folks.. who's joining me for a chat?
Counting down the days... 📸 Zyanya Lorenzo
Have you seen the official video for The Reason Why yet..? 😊
Working in the shadows..
📸 @ishashahphotography
